{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0193jW2WxyAdyaqEfX3ZcLSf","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# @alejandrocantero/kanbamd\n2\t\n3\tTypeScript package for managing Kanban boards stored as Markdown files with frontmatter and column folders.\n4\t\n5\t## Install\n6\t\n7\t```sh\n8\tnpm install @alejandrocantero/kanbamd\n9\t```\n10\t\n11\t## Board Layout\n12\t\n13\t```txt\n14\tboard/\n15\t  todo/\n16\t    fix-login.md\n17\t  doing/\n18\t  done/\n19\t```\n20\t\n21\tEach card is a `.md` file:\n22\t\n23\t```md\n24\t---\n25\ttitle: Fix login\n26\ttags:\n27\t  - bug\n28\torder: 1\n29\tpriority: high\n30\t---\n31\t\n32\tMarkdown body.\n33\t```\n34\t\n35\t## Usage\n36\t\n37\t```ts\n38\timport { Kanbamd } from \"@alejandrocantero/kanbamd\";\n39\t\n40\ttype ProjectFields = {\n41\t  priority?: \"low\" | \"medium\" | \"high\";\n42\t};\n43\t\n44\tconst board = new Kanbamd<ProjectFields>({\n45\t  root: \"./board\",\n46\t  columns: [\"todo\", \"doing\", \"done\"],\n47\t  createRoot: false,\n48\t  createColumns: true\n49\t});\n50\t\n51\tawait board.init();\n52\t\n53\tconst card = await board.createCard(\"todo\", {\n54\t  title: \"Fix login\",\n55\t  tags: [\"bug\"],\n56\t  body: \"OAuth callback fails.\",\n57\t  frontmatter: {\n58\t    priority: \"high\"\n59\t  }\n60\t});\n61\t\n62\tawait board.moveCard(\n63\t  { column: \"todo\", id: card.id },\n64\t  { column: \"doing\" }\n65\t);\n66\t\n67\tawait board.reorderCard({ column: \"doing\", id: card.id }, 0);\n68\t\n69\tconst results = await board.searchCards({\n70\t  query: \"logn callback\",\n71\t  tags: [\"bug\"]\n72\t});\n73\t```\n74\t\n75\t## Memory Storage\n76\t\n77\t```ts\n78\tconst board = new Kanbamd({\n79\t  storage: \"memory\",\n80\t  columns: [\"todo\", \"doing\", \"done\"]\n81\t});\n82\t\n83\tawait board.init();\n84\t```\n85\t\n86\t## Reserved Frontmatter\n87\t\n88\tThese fields are managed by Kanbamd and cannot be provided through custom frontmatter:\n89\t\n90\t- `title`\n91\t- `tags`\n92\t- `order`\n93\t\n94\tFilesystem metadata is exposed as `createdAt` and `updatedAt`.\n95\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d22e3197-cafa-48fe-8f3e-bcff61c66b02","uuid":"1cad18b4-c224-4b4d-811b-43309e0f4fff","timestamp":"2026-05-03T16:51:28.686Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.md","content":"# @alejandrocantero/kanbamd\n\nTypeScript package for managing Kanban boards stored as Markdown files with frontmatter and column folders.\n\n## Install\n\n```sh\nnpm install @alejandrocantero/kanbamd\n```\n\n## Board Layout\n\n```txt\nboard/\n  todo/\n    fix-login.md\n  doing/\n  done/\n```\n\nEach card is a `.md` file:\n\n```md\n---\ntitle: Fix login\ntags:\n  - bug\norder: 1\npriority: high\n---\n\nMarkdown body.\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```ts\nimport { Kanbamd } from \"@alejandrocantero/kanbamd\";\n\ntype ProjectFields = {\n  priority?: \"low\" | \"medium\" | \"high\";\n};\n\nconst board = new Kanbamd<ProjectFields>({\n  root: \"./board\",\n  columns: [\"todo\", \"doing\", \"done\"],\n  createRoot: false,\n  createColumns: true\n});\n\nawait board.init();\n\nconst card = await board.createCard(\"todo\", {\n  title: \"Fix login\",\n  tags: [\"bug\"],\n  body: \"OAuth callback fails.\",\n  frontmatter: {\n    priority: \"high\"\n  }\n});\n\nawait board.moveCard(\n  { column: \"todo\", id: card.id },\n  { column: \"doing\" }\n);\n\nawait board.reorderCard({ column: \"doing\", id: card.id }, 0);\n\nconst results = await board.searchCards({\n  query: \"logn callback\",\n  tags: [\"bug\"]\n});\n```\n\n## Memory Storage\n\n```ts\nconst board = new Kanbamd({\n  storage: \"memory\",\n  columns: [\"todo\", \"doing\", \"done\"]\n});\n\nawait board.init();\n```\n\n## Reserved Frontmatter\n\nThese fields are managed by Kanbamd and cannot be provided through custom frontmatter:\n\n- `title`\n- `tags`\n- `order`\n\nFilesystem metadata is exposed as `createdAt` and `updatedAt`.\n","numLines":95,"startLine":1,"totalLines":95}}}
